Paper: hep-th/0112107

Date: 2001-12-12

Title: About The Enhancon Mechanism

Authors: P. Merlatti

Comments: To appear in the proceedings of the RTN meeting ``The Quantum

Structure of Spacetime and the Geometric Nature of FundamentalInteractions'', (Corfu`, September 2001)Journal-ref: Fortsch.Phys. 50 (2002) 936-941

I study the enhancon mechanism for fractional D-branes in conifold andorbifold backgrounds and show how it can resolve the ``repulson'' singularityof these geometries. In particular I show that the consistency of the excisionprocess requires that the interior space be not empty.